It is like the cleric Complete Heal breastplate it was not a bug, it was intended, but the power it had was just not realized.  Using a few of them with with an infinite CH cycle was not intended and they fixed it.  They did not go and make every mob in the game hit 10x harder to address the issue and make it harder for every other player in the game.  No they just addressed the real problem.<br>
  <br>
Adding the random summoning mobs is just lazy and could be a sign of how issues will be addressed in the future (cut back on resources).  If they continue to fix problems by throwing in hacks with just switching a flag on mobs to make them able to summon, the game will soon become unplayable or no longer fun.<br>
